			<span class="vector-toc-numb">6</span>Presidencies of W. Wallace Smith and Wallace B. Smith</div>
		</a>
		
		<ul id="toc-Presidencies_of_W._Wallace_Smith_and_Wallace_B._Smith-sublist" class="vector-toc-list">
		</ul>
	</li>
	<li id="toc-Presidency_of_W._Grant_McMurray"
		class="vector-toc-list-item vector-toc-level-1 vector-toc-list-item-expanded">
